description:
(Part 2 of 7) Revelation 7:1-3 describes four mighty angels standing on the four corners of the earth holding back four fierce winds from devastating planet Earth. Their grip is loosening. Even now, the winds are starting to blow. Discover more about these winds and how to find protection in the coming storm.
